This runtime is a huge effort and deserve money to build and maintain it, but we believe you have the right to know what is running on your machine.
This runtime package can be totally dropped and replaced with an alternative implementation without affecting other parts of the system.

We encourage the community to create more efficient alternative, in other languages, or with different dependencies.

Contact us at https://www.robusta.build if you need more informations on architecture and technical partnerships.